%p 
  For the three categories below (shows, people, and organisations), please "tag"
  any references you can find on the item's documents. If the item is, for example,
  a flyer for a show, please make sure you add the show.

- form_for @item do |f|

  = f.error_messages

  %dl
    %dt Shows
    - for show in @item.shows
      %dd= show.name
    %dd
      %input.autocomplete{autocompleter('show'), :type => 'text'}
    %dd.notes Start typing a show's name

  %dl
    %dt People
    %dd
      %input.autocomplete{autocompleter('person'), :type => 'text'}
    %dd.notes Start typing a person's name

    %dt Organisations
    %dd
      %input.autocomplete{autocompleter('organisation'), :type => 'text'}
    %dd.notes Start typing an organisation's name

    %dt &nbsp;
    %dd.buttons
      %a.positive
        = icon 'tick'
        Save changes
